@startuml C4_Pattern_Loops
!include https://raw.githubusercontent.com/plantuml-stdlib/C4-PlantUML/master/C4_Component.puml

title YAWL Workflow Pattern - Loop Patterns

Boundary(loops, "Loop Execution Patterns") {
    Component(foreach_loop, "For-Each Loop", "Pattern", "Iterate collection")
    Component(while_loop, "While Loop", "Pattern", "Condition-based")
    Component(do_while, "Do-While Loop", "Pattern", "Execute-first")
    Component(loop_handler, "LoopHandler", "Manager", "Loop logic")
    Component(termination_check, "TerminationChecker", "Safety", "Loop termination")
}

Boundary(foreach_impl, "For-Each Implementation") {
    Component(collection, "Collection", "Data", "Items to iterate")
    Component(iterator, "Iterator", "State", "Current item")
    Component(loop_task, "LoopTask", "Body", "Execute per item")
    Component(completion_check, "CompletionChecker", "Logic", "Check done?")
}

foreach_impl --> loop_handler: Uses
loop_handler --> termination_check: Validates

Note as N1
For-Each: FOREACH item IN collection
While: WHILE condition()
Do-While: DO { task } WHILE condition()
Termination: Must exit eventually (safety)
End note

SHOW_LEGEND()
@enduml
